    "last_activity_date" : 1641060291,
    "last_edit_date" : 1641060291,
    "creation_date" : 1630646274,
    "answer_id" : 69039849,
    "question_id" : 69034879,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Finally, I can solve my issue.</p>\n<p>What was the problem?</p>\n<p>I had the following dependency in one module -</p>\n<pre><code>implementation &quot;androidx.core:core-ktx:+&quot;\n</code></pre>\n<p>but other modules, including the app module, had the following dependency</p>\n<pre><code>implementation &quot;androidx.core:core-ktx:1.6.0&quot;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Converting</p>\n<pre><code>implementation &quot;androidx.core:core-ktx:+&quot;\n</code></pre>\n<p>to</p>\n<pre><code>implementation &quot;androidx.core:core-ktx:1.6.0&quot;\n</code></pre>\n<p>solved my problem.</p>\n"
  }, {
