    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have found the solution. Enter this line of code above package in the app Gradle file.</p>\n<p>For Kotlin developers:</p>\n<pre><code>configurations.all {\n    resolutionStrategy { force 'androidx.core:core-ktx:1.6.0' }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lAE2k.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lAE2k.png\" alt=\"Screenshot of code with a red freehand circle\" /></a></p>\n<p>For Java developers</p>\n<pre><code>configurations.all {\n    resolutionStrategy { force 'androidx.core:core:1.6.0' }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
