    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Set both <code>compileSdkVersion</code> and <code>targetSdkVersion</code> to <code>31</code> in your <code>build.gradle(app)</code> file.</p>\n<pre><code>android {\n    compileSdkVersion 31 // &lt;-- This\n    defaultConfig {\n        applicationId &quot;com.example.app&quot;\n        targetSdkVersion 31 // &lt;-- and this too\n        // ...\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
