    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This issue is most often seen with libraries that declare</p>\n<p><code>implementation androidx.core:core-ktx:1.7.0-beta01</code></p>\n<p>The <code>minCompileSdk</code> is 31, but the <code>minSdkVersion</code> is significantly lower.</p>\n<p>Increasing the <code>compileSdk</code> of your project is enough to fix the issue. There is no need for overrides or even changing the <code>targetSdk</code>.</p>\n<pre><code>android {\n    compileSdk 31\n\n...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
